                        <p class="service-description">Special packages for businesses with discounted rates and priority service.</p>
                        <ul class="service-features">
                            <li><i data-lucide="check" class="feature-check"></i>Volume Discounts</li>
                            <li><i data-lucide="check" class="feature-check"></i>Priority Support</li>
                            <li><i data-lucide="check" class="feature-check"></i>Billing Solutions</li>
